      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to a standard that exceeds conventional expectations. This vehicle showcases a flawless exterior finish paired with an interior that retains its original showroom luster. Rigorously inspected for mechanical absolute integrity, it offers a driving experience indistinguishable from its initial delivery. This is an investment-grade acquisition for the most discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
